@c This file is include from install.texi and contains the descriptions for
@c package-specific enable/disable and with/without options

In addition, the following @command{configure} options, specific to the
@value{PACKAGE_TITLE} package are available:

@table @command
@item --disable-compat-os7
@opindex compat-os7
Disable @cite{OpenSS7} compatibility module.
When enabled, @value{PACKAGE_TITLE} will attempt to be as compatible as possible (witout replicating
any bugs) with the @cite{OpenSS7} documentation so that STREAMS drivers and modules written to
@cite{OpenSS7} specifications will compile with @value{PACKAGE_TITLE}.  When disabled, STREAMS
drivers and modules written for @cite{OpenSS7} will require porting in more respects.
This option defaults to @samp{enabled}.

